div.p: landing page will distinguish between customer and admin and will open authorizations accordingly. This difference will be defined in the scheme model in the user type attribute = customer/admin

user:
will be routed to his/her project's heatmap page and will be authorized to map corrollations between solutions and observations within that page.

p.span:
Admin:
will have authorization to view all the pages of the application - view all projects, add project, edit and delete projects, access to every project's heatmap.
